  "scrape_strategy_for_code": {
    "method": "Playwright sync",
    "steps": [
      "1. Navigate to region URL (e.g. https://saily.com/esim-africa/)",
      "2. Wait for page to load (networkidle)",
      "3. Extract plan text using regex on body.innerText: /(\\d+ GB|Unlimited GB)\\s*\\n\\s*(\\d+ days?)\\s*\\n\\s*(US\\$[\\d.]+)/",
      "4. For discounted plans, also capture original price: second US$ amount after the discounted one",
      "5. For Unlimited plans: find <select> with day options, iterate each <option>, select it, wait 600ms, read updated price",
      "6. Click 'View country list' button",
      "7. Extract countries from body.innerText using: /Country list\\s*\\n([\\s\\S]*?)(?:\\d+\\s*GB\\n|\\nKey features|\\nDescription)/",
      "8. Remove first line (region name header) from country list",
      "9. Clean country list: filter lines with length 1-60 chars"
    ]
  }
